43/* https://github.com/harfbuzz/harfbuzz/issues/1734 */
44/**
45 * HB_MATH_GLYPH_PART_FLAG_EXTENDER:
46 *
47 * Use #HB_OT_MATH_GLYPH_PART_FLAG_EXTENDER instead.
48 *
49 * Deprecated: 2.5.1
50 */
51#define HB_MATH_GLYPH_PART_FLAG_EXTENDER HB_OT_MATH_GLYPH_PART_FLAG_EXTENDER
52
53/* https://github.com/harfbuzz/harfbuzz/pull/3417 */
54/**
55 * HB_OT_MATH_SCRIPT:
56 *
57 * Use #HB_SCRIPT_MATH or #HB_OT_TAG_MATH_SCRIPT instead.
58 *
59 * <note>Previous versions of this documentation recommended passing
60 * #HB_OT_MATH_SCRIPT to hb_buffer_set_script() to enable math shaping, but this
61 * usage is no longer supported. Use #HB_SCRIPT_MATH instead.</note>
62 *
63 * Since: 1.3.3
64 * Deprecated: 3.4.0
65 */
66#define HB_OT_MATH_SCRIPT HB_OT_TAG_MATH_SCRIPT

97/**
98 * HB_OT_VAR_NO_AXIS_INDEX:
99 *
100 * Do not use.
101 *
102 * Since: 1.4.2
103 * Deprecated: 2.2.0
104 */
105#define HB_OT_VAR_NO_AXIS_INDEX 0xFFFFFFFFu
106
107/**
108 * hb_ot_var_axis_t:
109 * @tag: axis tag
110 * @name_id: axis name identifier
111 * @min_value: minimum value of the axis
112 * @default_value: default value of the axis
113 * @max_value: maximum value of the axis
114 *
115 * Use #hb_ot_var_axis_info_t instead.
116 *
117 * Since: 1.4.2
118 * Deprecated: 2.2.0
119 */
120typedef struct hb_ot_var_axis_t {
121 hb_tag_t tag;
122 hb_ot_name_id_t name_id;
123 float min_value;
124 float default_value;
125 float max_value;
126} hb_ot_var_axis_t;
127
128HB_DEPRECATED_FOR (hb_ot_var_get_axis_infos)
129HB_EXTERN unsigned int
130hb_ot_var_get_axes (hb_face_t *face,
131 unsigned int start_offset,
132 unsigned int *axes_count /* IN/OUT */,
133 hb_ot_var_axis_t *axes_array /* OUT */);
134
135HB_DEPRECATED_FOR (hb_ot_var_find_axis_info)
136HB_EXTERN hb_bool_t
137hb_ot_var_find_axis (hb_face_t *face,
138 hb_tag_t axis_tag,
139 unsigned int *axis_index,
140 hb_ot_var_axis_t *axis_info);
